        "description": "Escape Morgue is a fun and scary VR game where you explore a creepy morgue to find hidden notes. But be careful! A ghost is lurking around and will chase you if it sees you. Your mission is to find all the notes and escape the morgue before the ghost catches you.\n\n\nThis game is perfect for anyone who loves a good scare. You'll feel like you're really in a haunted morgue, searching for clues and trying to stay safe from the ghost. It's a thrilling adventure that will keep you on the edge of your seat.\n\n**Key Features:** \n\n- **Exciting VR Experience:** Feel like you're really in a spooky morgue.\n- **Challenging Gameplay:** Find all the hidden notes while avoiding the ghost.\n- **Thrilling Atmosphere:** Hear creepy sounds and see scary sights that will give you chills.\n- **Perfect for Horror Fans:** If you love ghost stories and haunted places, this game is for you.\n\nGet ready to test your bravery and see if you can escape the haunted morgue! Can you find all the notes and outsmart the ghost? Try **Escape Morgue** and find out!",
